h3. +Summary+
From the [Importing data from Bugzilla documentation|https://confluence.atlassian.com/adminjiraserver071/importing-data-from-bugzilla-802592828.html], it stated that there is an option for user to either map or not map the components from Bugzilla to JIRA when import. 
{quote}
You can choose to have the importer automatically create your Bugzilla component(s) in JIRA, or choose to have bugs imported into no component in JIRA.
{quote}
But the interface of the importer for bugzilla does not provide any option for users to map or not map the components. According to this ticket (https://ecosystem.atlassian.net/browse/JIM-864), the feature is not provided in bugzilla importer.  

h3. +Suggestion+
Update the documentation to avoid customer confusion.

